CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F377A1782053271
OL,3,CTeen wrongly arrested over mothers
OL,4,Csuicide attempt wins case against
OL,5,Cpolice
OL,7,FAn innocent teenager has won his legal
OL,8,Fcase against the Metropolitan Police
OL,9,Fafter he was wrongly arrested for the
OL,10,Fattempted murder of his mother in
OL,11,FSouth London.
OL,13,FA jury found officers discriminated
OL,14,Fagainst 16 year old Daryl McLune
OL,15,Fbecause of his race.
OL,17,FHe was held for 23 hours after his
OL,18,Fmother attempted to take her own life.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/9
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,378,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F377A1782053271
OL,3,CTeen wrongly arrested over mothers
OL,4,Csuicide attempt wins case against
OL,5,Cpolice
OL,7,FThe court found the Metropolitan
OL,8,FPolice conduct towards Daryl McLune
OL,9,Famounted to inhuman and degrading
OL,10,Ftreatment, in breach of his human
OL,11,Frights.
OL,13,FOn 25 July 2021 Daryl, who was 16 at
OL,14,Fthe time, returned home following a
OL,15,Fcall from his father to find his
OL,16,Fmother fighting for her life on the
OL,17,Fground outside their home, having
OL,18,Fjumped from the roof of their block of
OL,19,Fflats.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/9
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,378,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F377A1782053271
OL,3,CTeen wrongly arrested over mothers
OL,4,Csuicide attempt wins case against
OL,5,Cpolice
OL,7,FDespite officers seeing Daryl cycle to
OL,8,Fthe scene after them, they arrested
OL,9,Fhim for the attempted murder of his
OL,10,Fmother.
OL,12,FThe teenager was handcuffed in front
OL,13,Fof his neighbours and taken to
OL,14,FWandsworth Police Station. He was held
OL,15,Fovernight for twenty-three hours, his
OL,16,Ffirst experience of being detained by
OL,17,Fthe police.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/9
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,378,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F377A1782053271
OL,3,CTeen wrongly arrested over mothers
OL,4,Csuicide attempt wins case against
OL,5,Cpolice
OL,7,FDaryl remained in handcuffs for five
OL,8,Fhours until police took forensic
OL,9,Fsamples from his hands, which were
OL,10,Fnever processed or submitted.
OL,12,FPolice officers reportedly refused to
OL,13,Ftell Daryl whether his mother was
OL,14,Falive or dead, or to give him any
OL,15,Finformation about her condition.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/9
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,378,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F377A1782053271
OL,3,CTeen wrongly arrested over mothers
OL,4,Csuicide attempt wins case against
OL,5,Cpolice
OL,7,FThe verdict comes during a civil trial
OL,8,Fat which the court heard of the
OL,9,Fprofound impact of the arrest on
OL,10,FDaryl, who had been a diligent student
OL,11,Fbut ended up dropping out of school
OL,12,Ffollowing his arrest.
OL,14,FThe judge, His Honour Judge Holmes,
OL,15,Fwill now determine what damages should
OL,16,Fbe paid to Daryl and is expected to
OL,17,Fmake a decision in the near future.
OL,19,FDaryl McLune said:
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G5/9
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,378,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F377A1782053271
OL,3,CTeen wrongly arrested over mothers
OL,4,Csuicide attempt wins case against
OL,5,Cpolice
OL,7,F"I am pleased and grateful to the jury
OL,8,Ffor considering my case so carefully
OL,9,Fand for reaching the decision that
OL,10,Fthey have.
OL,12,F"I have waited a long time for this
OL,13,Fvindication and whilst I will never
OL,14,Fforget these events, having the jury
OL,15,Fconfirm I should never have been
OL,16,Farrested, will I hope help me to try
OL,17,Fto move on and recover from this
OL,18,Fincident.
OL,20,FMegan Phillips, representing Daryl
OL,21,Fsaid:
OL,26,@oD@AOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G6/9
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,378,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37707
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F377A1782053271
OL,3,CTeen wrongly arrested over mothers
OL,4,Csuicide attempt wins case against
OL,5,Cpolice
OL,7,F"This case shows the true face of two-
OL,8,Ftier policing in this country, where a
OL,9,Fyoung black teenager can be unlawfully
OL,10,Farrested for the attempted murder of
OL,11,Fhis own mother, in circumstances where
OL,12,Fthe court has found that the officers
OL,13,Fdid not genuinely suspect him of
OL,14,Fcommitting any offence and where their
OL,15,Fbehaviour was infected by race
OL,16,Fdiscrimination.
OL,26,@oD@AOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G7/9
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,378,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37708
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F377A1782053271
OL,3,CTeen wrongly arrested over mothers
OL,4,Csuicide attempt wins case against
OL,5,Cpolice
OL,7,F"Daryl was a child in crisis who
OL,8,Fshould have been offered support as he
OL,9,Fsuffered the shock and grief of seeing
OL,10,Fhis mother fighting for her life with
OL,11,Fcatastrophic injuries.
OL,13,F"Instead, he was wrongly treated as a
OL,14,Fsuspect because of his race."
OL,16,FA spokesperson for the Met said:
OL,18,F"We are aware of the findings of a
OL,19,Fjury in a civil trial relating to the
OL,20,Farrest and detention of a boy in July
OL,21,F2021.
OL,26,@vD@]O]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G8/9
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,378,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37709
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F377A1782053271
OL,3,CTeen wrongly arrested over mothers
OL,4,Csuicide attempt wins case against
OL,5,Cpolice
OL,7,F"We acknowledge how distressing it was
OL,8,Ffor the boy to have been arrested in
OL,9,Fthese tragic circumstances.
OL,11,F"The Met is committed to tackling all
OL,12,Fforms of discrimination, including
OL,13,Funconscious bias. We know cases like
OL,14,Fthis damage the trust communities have
OL,15,Fin us and we will be considering the
OL,16,Foutcome carefully."
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G9/9
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
